OL,3,CCouple celebrate Platinum wedding
OL,4,Canniversary at care home
OL,6,FA couple from Newport on the Isle of
OL,7,FWight have celebrated their 70th
OL,8,Fanniversary at their care home.
OL,10,FMary Clarke, 90, and her husband John,
OL,11,F95, met by chance at a dance hall in
OL,12,FRyde back in 1953, and said it was
OL,13,Flove at first sight for both of them.
OL,15,FSeven decades on, they say the secret
OL,16,Fto a long happy marriage is having
OL,17,Fboth common and separate interests.
