OL,3,CCouple celebrate Platinum wedding
OL,4,Canniversary at care home
OL,6,FThe couple, who live in a sheltered
OL,7,Fhousing scheme run by The Abbeyfield
OL,8,FSociety were joined by friends, family
OL,9,Fand staff at their home to enjoy a
OL,10,Fbuffet and a Platinum Anniversary
OL,11,Fcake, made by their housekeeper.
OL,13,FJohn and Mary married in Nottingham in
OL,14,FMarch 1954, which they cite as their
OL,15,Fmost romantic moment.
OL,17,FMary and John have made lots of happy
OL,18,Fmemories since, and together they have
OL,19,Fraised their three sons, Paul, John
OL,20,Fand Alun.
